	* printf-parse.h (FLAG_LOCALIZED): New macro.
	* printf-parse.c (PRINTF_PARSE): Handle the 'I' flag.
	* vasnprintf.c (VASNPRINTF): Pass the 'I' flag on to the system's
	snprintf function.

