	localename: Make aware of thread locale.
	* localename.c: Include <limits.h>, <stddef.h>, <xlocale.h>,
	<langinfo.h>, glthread/lock.h.
	(SIZE_BITS): New macro.
	(string_hash): New function.
	(struct hash_node): New type.
